787</guid><pubDate>Thu, 10 Sep 2009 17:30:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:updated>2010-01-25T23:11:11.860+05:30</atom:updated><category domain='http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#'>portfolio</category><title>PortFolio</title><description>A Developer! And the portfolio up in a Blogger! ? I know that's kind of being stupid.&lt;br /&gt;Well I have been planning to move over custom domain, but until then , Since you are already in my Portfolio @ Blogger.. Why don't you just have a look at it, may be I can be the developer for your next project and share a coffee on the same table!&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="background-color: #ffe599;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;1. Wordpress website&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;b&gt;Features:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;The header with the and links are FIXED on the page and never to scroll.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;The content of the page&amp;nbsp; scrolls UNDER the header.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;The background of the page is also fixed and does not scroll just like the header does.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Content area is 1 column (800px wide) centered with NO sidebar and NO WordPress content or widgets whatsoever on any pages.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;b&gt;Posted:&lt;/b&gt; &lt;i&gt;25 jan 2010 &lt;/i&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_2RdcFsdvQws/S13V3imYEWI/AAAAAAAAA4A/c-OD6NnuMVM/s1600-h/clintenglish.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"&gt;&lt;img border="0" height="409" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_2RdcFsdvQws/S13V3imYEWI/AAAAAAAAA4A/c-OD6NnuMVM/s640/clintenglish.jpg" width="640" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleuser